CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780348266
OL,3,CMedical students at Manchester
OL,4,CUniversity report years of sexual
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,FMore than 30 women have reported
OL,8,Fissues of sexual harassment and
OL,9,Fintimidation among the student cohort
OL,10,Fat the University of Manchester's
OL,11,Fmedical school.
OL,13,FIt comes after a medical student wrote
OL,14,Fan open letter to the University of
OL,15,FManchester calling for a formal review
OL,16,Finto sexism within the School of
OL,17,FMedical Sciences.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780348266
OL,3,CMedical students at Manchester
OL,4,CUniversity report years of sexual
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,FCharlotte Buttercase, 24 said she has
OL,8,Fbeen subjected to repeated sexual
OL,9,Fharassment and intimidation while
OL,10,Fstudying medicine. She believes women
OL,11,Fin a similar situation do not feel
OL,12,Fempowered to speak up.
OL,14,FCharlotte said: "There is a woman like
OL,15,Fme at every University and I will
OL,16,Fcontinue to say that, she just needs
OL,17,Fto be given her voice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780348266
OL,3,CMedical students at Manchester
OL,4,CUniversity report years of sexual
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,F"I think this issue is huge and 30 is
OL,8,Fa modest estimate of how deeply I
OL,9,Fthink this runs and how many women
OL,10,Fhave in fact suffered this and they
OL,11,Fdon't feel empowered to speak up, seek
OL,12,Fany kind of accountability from the
OL,13,Fperpetrator because the pattern
OL,14,Fsuggests they will get off scot free"
OL,16,FThe letter says: "Gathered evidence
OL,17,Fdemonstrates that for several years,
OL,18,Fwomen have been receiving anonymous
OL,19,Fcalls, during which where they are
OL,20,Fsubjected to scare tactics and sexual
OL,21,Fharassment."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780348266
OL,3,CMedical students at Manchester
OL,4,CUniversity report years of sexual
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,F"These range from telling them they
OL,8,Fare being watched, to asking them to
OL,9,Fperform sexual favours or indeed
OL,10,Fscreaming gender-based slurs, all
OL,11,Ftargeted to moments of vulnerability,
OL,12,Fin the early hours of the morning."
OL,14,FCharlotte has now completed her final
OL,15,Fyear studying medicine, her letter has
OL,16,Fmore than 1,000 signatures.
OL,18,FIt goes on to ask for action from the
OL,19,FUniversity, saying:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780348266
OL,3,CMedical students at Manchester
OL,4,CUniversity report years of sexual
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,F"To date, 15 women, across multiple
OL,8,Fcohorts have contributed to my police
OL,9,Freport of harassment. We urge the
OL,10,FUniversity of Manchester to respond
OL,11,Ffirmly, and swiftly, in staunch
OL,12,Fopposition to this practice as not
OL,13,Fonly being against the code of the
OL,14,Fschool, but the institution, and in
OL,15,Ffact the very oath sworn and standard
OL,16,Fdemanded of those entering a career in
OL,17,FMedicine."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780348266
OL,3,CMedical students at Manchester
OL,4,CUniversity report years of sexual
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,F'We urge you as President and Vice-
OL,8,FChancellor of the University of
OL,9,FManchester, to initiate a formal
OL,10,Freview of sexism within the School of
OL,11,FMedical Sciences."
OL,13,F"Such proceedings to include
OL,14,Finvestigation into the number of
OL,15,Fperpetrators of sexual violence
OL,16,Fpermitted to enter and continue their
OL,17,Fstudies on professional courses."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780348266
OL,3,CMedical students at Manchester
OL,4,CUniversity report years of sexual
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,FProfessor Ashley Blom, Vice-President
OL,8,Fand Dean of the Faculty of Biology,
OL,9,FMedicine and Health at the University
OL,10,Fof Manchester said:
OL,12,F"The issues raised are deeply
OL,13,Fconcerning, and we are treating them
OL,14,Fwith the utmost seriousness. No member
OL,15,Fof our community should ever
OL,16,Fexperience behaviour that makes them
OL,17,Ffeel unsafe, intimidated or harassed.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780348266
OL,3,CMedical students at Manchester
OL,4,CUniversity report years of sexual
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,F"Our immediate priority is supporting
OL,8,Fthe students affected. We have
OL,9,Flaunched a formal investigation into
OL,10,Fthe specific allegations raised, and
OL,11,Fwe are also undertaking a wider review
OL,12,Fof the cultural and systemic issues
OL,13,Fidentified. We will continue to take
OL,14,Fwhatever action is necessary to
OL,15,Faddress the issues identified and
OL,16,Fdeliver meaningful, lasting change.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780348266
OL,3,CMedical students at Manchester
OL,4,CUniversity report years of sexual
OL,5,Charassment
OL,7,F"We know that our students and
OL,8,Fcolleagues must have confidence that
OL,9,Fconcerns will be listened to, taken
OL,10,Fseriously and acted upon. I want to
OL,11,Fthank everyone who has come forward
OL,12,Fand shown courage in speaking up. I
OL,13,Fwould strongly encourage anyone who
OL,14,Fhas experienced or witnessed similar
OL,15,Fbehaviour to report it so appropriate
OL,16,Faction can be taken."
OL,26,@xD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
